      <title>巴基斯坦的通货膨胀率在3月的1％以下的新鲜低下</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/pakistan-s-inflation-eases-to-a-fresh-low-below-1-in-march</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦的通货膨胀率上个月放缓至七年来的最低水平，尽管决策者将对全球贸易中断的价格上涨的风险保持谨慎。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/pakistan-s-inflation-eases-to-a-fresh-low-below-1-in-march</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 09:22:42 GMT</pubDate>
